# 📊 Sales Data Analysis

This project analyzes fictional retail sales data to discover insights in product performance, regional trends, and time-based sales patterns.

## 📁 Dataset
- `sales_data.csv` contains simulated sales records of 5 products across 4 regions over 6 months.

## 📈 Key Insights
- Total sales by product and region
- Monthly sales trend analysis
- Heatmap visualization of product-region relationships

## 🧰 Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib & Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook

